      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Get ready for your next great project! This car is the perfect find for someone who loves to roll up their sleeves and bring a vehicle back to its former glory. While it currently shows significant wear and will require some dedicated mechanical attention and TLC to get it back on the road, it offers a fantastic foundation for a restoration enthusiast at a great value!",
