    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable companion for your daily commutes? This dependable vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! It shows some honest wear from its time on the road, but it still delivers a solid performance that you can trust to get you where you need to go. It's a great value for anyone seeking a functional, straightforward ride!",
      "price": 20500.0,
